[
  {
    "id": 17563,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "1",
    "text": "Then Eliphaz the Temanite answered,"
  },
  {
    "id": 17564,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "2",
    "text": "“Can a man be profitable to God?"
  },
  {
    "id": 17565,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "3",
    "text": "Is it any pleasure to the Almighty that you are righteous?"
  },
  {
    "id": 17566,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "4",
    "text": "Is it for your piety that he reproves you,"
  },
  {
    "id": 17567,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "5",
    "text": "Isn’t your wickedness great?"
  },
  {
    "id": 17568,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "6",
    "text": "For you have taken pledges from your brother for nothing,"
  },
  {
    "id": 17569,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "7",
    "text": "You haven’t given water to the weary to drink,"
  },
  {
    "id": 17570,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "8",
    "text": "But as for the mighty man, he had the earth."
  },
  {
    "id": 17571,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "9",
    "text": "You have sent widows away empty,"
  },
  {
    "id": 17572,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "10",
    "text": "Therefore snares are around you."
  },
  {
    "id": 17573,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "11",
    "text": "or darkness, so that you can not see,"
  },
  {
    "id": 17574,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "12",
    "text": "“Isn’t God in the heights of heaven?"
  },
  {
    "id": 17575,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "13",
    "text": "You say, ‘What does God know?"
  },
  {
    "id": 17576,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "14",
    "text": "Thick clouds are a covering to him, so that he doesn’t see."
  },
  {
    "id": 17577,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "15",
    "text": "Will you keep the old way,"
  },
  {
    "id": 17578,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "16",
    "text": "who were snatched away before their time,"
  },
  {
    "id": 17579,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "17",
    "text": "who said to God, ‘Depart from us!’"
  },
  {
    "id": 17580,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "18",
    "text": "Yet he filled their houses with good things,"
  },
  {
    "id": 17581,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "19",
    "text": "The righteous see it, and are glad."
  },
  {
    "id": 17582,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "20",
    "text": "saying, ‘Surely those who rose up against us are cut off."
  },
  {
    "id": 17583,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "21",
    "text": "“Acquaint yourself with him now, and be at peace."
  },
  {
    "id": 17584,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "22",
    "text": "Please receive instruction from his mouth,"
  },
  {
    "id": 17585,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "23",
    "text": "If you return to the Almighty, you will be built up,"
  },
  {
    "id": 17586,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "24",
    "text": "Lay your treasure in the dust,"
  },
  {
    "id": 17587,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "25",
    "text": "The Almighty will be your treasure,"
  },
  {
    "id": 17588,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "26",
    "text": "For then you will delight yourself in the Almighty,"
  },
  {
    "id": 17589,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "27",
    "text": "You will make your prayer to him, and he will hear you."
  },
  {
    "id": 17590,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "28",
    "text": "You will also decree a thing, and it will be established to you."
  },
  {
    "id": 17591,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "29",
    "text": "When they cast down, you will say, ‘be lifted up.’"
  },
  {
    "id": 17592,
    "book": "job                                     ",
    "chapter": "22",
    "verse": "30",
    "text": "He will even deliver him who is not innocent."
  }
]